that exist in a critical space.

00:23:40.670 --> 00:23:44.007 position:50% align:center line:84%
The origin of Spirits.
The mystery of Shido Itsuka.

00:23:44.090 --> 00:23:46.468 position:50% align:center line:84%
All of this shall become clear.

